node.text: So so so excited... and overwhelmed that we get to perform at all these beautiful places, now including my hometown!! oh my gosh I'm freakking ouutt hahahah😭 We're finally coming guys🖤 Love you so much

node.text: 2018 was a blast! I love you Blinks and I'm so thankful for my members @blackpinkofficial. Thank you for making it a really fun year for me. And thank you to all the amazing people in my life who help me to become a better person everyday and to all the adults that I can always look up to and learn from (you know who u all are😽). I'm so thankful when I think of all the beautiful people around me. Including all of my fans ❤️ In 2019, I hope to be able to make it up to everyone of you by being the best version of me that I can❤️ I hope everyone has a safe night and starts the new year on a positive and healthy note! HAPPY NEW YEAR MY LOVES! 모두 새해 복 많이 받으세용! 🙇‍♀️
